cat
# Interpreter for 'vpn-switch help' command (main help/usage)
# Terminal function that displays help text directly to user
#
# Default value: "cat"
#   Displays usage information without executing commands
#   The usage() function outputs formatted help text
#
# The help command is informational only - it does not generate
# executable commands, so it should use 'cat' to display directly
# to the terminal rather than 'sh' to execute.
#
# Phase 2.7: Help system uses cat interpreter for direct display
